name: Wes Janson (V)
Lore: 'Served for many years as a gunner with friend Jek Porkins in the Tierfon Yellow Aces. Expert marksmanship helped the Alliance earn some of its earliest victories.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting Red 3, it gains [Nav Computer] and Wes draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. While aboard a starship or vehicle, its total weapon destiny is +1; if with Jek and it hits a target, opponent loses 1 Force from Reserve Deck.(Original concept by Alexander Sheynis - Berkeley V-Lite 2005)',
